<h2 class="videoHeader">MHacks hackathon</h2>
<h4 class="videoPostDate">Friday, February 8, 2013 10:07 a.m.</h4>
<span><a class="closeX lbClose" href="#">Close </a></span>
<div class="vidHolder"><iframe class="shadow" frameborder="0" height="386" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/D6_bF3dFEAI?rel=0" width="700"></iframe></div>
